Company Overview of Trustmark Investment Advisors, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Trustmark Investment Advisors, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to banking and thrift institutions and investment companies, individuals, institutions, foundations, endowments, and charitable organizations. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm launches and managed equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of mid-cap and large-cap companies to create its equity portfolios. For its fixed income portion, the firm invests in U.S. Governmen...
Trustmark Investment Advisors, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to banking and thrift institutions and investment companies, individuals, institutions, foundations, endowments, and charitable organizations. It manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm launches and managed equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of mid-cap and large-cap companies to create its equity portfolios. For its fixed income portion, the firm invests in U.S. Government, Agency, mortgage-related, and high-quality corporate securities. It employs a combination of qualitative and quantitative analysis to make its investments. The firm was founded on June 1, 2011 and is based in Jackson, Mississippi with an additional office in Jackson, Mississippi. Trustmark Investment Advisors, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Trustmark National Bank.
Detailed Description


